divs: Sighting DetailsLast february we have a trip to el Nevado de Toluca, one of the popular mountains that are in Mexico. We climbed almot till the top and start taking pictures. After a couple of weeks we were viewing the photo album and something caught our attention we zoom in and zoom out and we think that probably its a legal UFO. At that time in the top of the mountain we didnt hear any noise or even see anything weird, as I told we notice the UFO in only one pic of the hundreds we took in that family trip.
